title: Vanaja Girija
subTitle: Sisters Vanaja and Girija believe they were abandoned by their father due to the influence of a man named Ramanathan. The duo vow to alienate Ramanathan from his family as he did to theirs.

title: Chinna Thayee
subTitle: Rasamma strives to ensure a proper life for her daughter Chinna, who is born out of wedlock. But her worst fear comes true when her daughter follows her footsteps and falls in love with a rich man.

title: Vesham
subTitle: Circumstances force a famous singer, Ashok, to work at a local music shop, where he meets his fan, Devi. Soon, she decides to approach Ashok to teach Raja, who has misbehaved with her, a lesson.

title: Thangappathakkam
subTitle: SP Choudhury, a police officer, and his rebelious son's relationship becomes strained after the son gets arrested for illegal activities.

title: Theertha Karaiyinile
subTitle: A jobless man meets a tuberculosis patient on the threshold of death, and goes to the patient's village pretending to be him. There, he navigates his way around greedy relatives and falls in love with a girl.

title: Ramakrishna
subTitle: Ramakrishna, a millionaire, stays with his mother and is not in touch with anyone from his family. After her death, he decides to go to the village in search of his long lost relatives.

title: Vetri
subTitle: Vijay loves challenges and goes to any limit to win them. But one such challenge lands him in prison on a murder charge, as he was used as a pawn to kill his professor.

title: Thalattu Padava
subTitle: Raja, an educated young man, works as a driver for a rich client and gets harassed by his granddaughter. When she realises how learned he is, she falls in love with him and wishes to marry him.
